&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Integrantes do Grupo Olho Latino participam da mostra Fronteras Nómades - Chile, Brasil e Peru.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: right;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost/grupo/index.php?option=com_content&amp;amp;view=article&amp;amp;id=80:-a-mostra-fronteras-nomades-ii-chega-ao-brasil&amp;amp;catid=54&quot;&gt;Leia Mais&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
