		<title>5ª Bienal Nacional de Gravura - Olho Latino</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost/grupo/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=61:5o-bienal-nacional-de-gravura-olho-latino&amp;catid=37:2011"/>
